\pard\plain \tx0\fi360\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Ps::0>The lingering weight of the previous moment dissipated as Evan, with practiced ease, compartmentalized his pain. A playful grin spread across his face, chasing away the shadows. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Well, that got heavy fast,\u8221\'94 he joked. \u8220\'93We should get honorary awards for spectacularly breaking all the first-date rules.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 Maggie smiled, her own tension easing. She was happy to follow his lead back into lighter territory. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Absolutely,\u8221\'94 she agreed. \u8220\'93Maybe they\u8217\'92ll even name a rule after us!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Perfect.\u8221\'94 Evan\u8217\'92s grin widened. \u8220\'93Now, it\u8217\'92s time for the real test \endash  the compatibility challenge. Are you in?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 Intrigued, Maggie tilted her head. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Oh, this sounds interesting. Bring it on!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s not a make-or-break test,\u8221\'94 Evan clarified, a hint of mock seriousness in his tone. \u8220\'93When I left you ladies earlier, I snuck over to the ticket booth. They have these wristbands - the kind usually seen on the younger crowd. They let you go on all the rides as many times as you want.\u8221\'94 Maggie\u8217\'92s laughter bubbled over, the sound light and cheerful. He paused, a playful glint in his eye. \u8220\'93I know, I know, not exactly a sophisticated date for grown-ups like us. But honestly, I really want to go on all the rides! I\u8217\'92ll completely understand if you\u8217\'92d rather do something a bit more...\u8221\'94 he searched for the word, \u8220\'93age-appropriate.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 A spark of amusement lit up Maggie\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s eyes. She loved how easily Evan could laugh at himself. It was a refreshing contrast to the men she usually dated. \u8220\'93Age-appropriate? Who wants to be a responsible adult?\u8221\'94 she teased. \u8220\'93Wristbands and carnival rides sound perfect!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 Evan let out a relieved chuckle. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Excellent! That\u8217\'92s compatibility test number one passed with flying colors. Now, onto challenge number two...\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 Maggie leaned in, her eyes twinkling. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Another challenge? I can\u8217\'92t wait.\u8221\'94}
